        <updateDate>2014-10-09T17:09:56Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Housing for Persons With AIDS Modernization Act of 2014 - Amends the AIDS Housing Opportunity Act to revise the formula and terms for allocations of grants to states, local governments, and nonprofit organizations for housing programs for persons with acquired immune deficiency syndrome (AIDS) (as under current law), as well as those with human immunodeficiency virus (HIV).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
